abstract: Russian space agency succeeds in inaugural launch of unmanned Soyuz rocket from Vostochny Cosmodrome, despite last minute technical glitch that delayed blastoff; Pres Vladimir V Putin is in attendance.
lead_paragraph: Russia’s space agency had postponed the inaugural launch of a rocket from the Vostochny Cosmodrome in the Far East, citing technical problems.

headline.main: With Vladimir Putin Waiting, Russian Rocket Launches Late
headline.print_headline: Glitch Delays Rocket Launch as Putin Visits Space Center
